{"tid":843210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"落馬洲清晨淪陷 200內地客不滿塞車 欲步行過關闖港邊境 被警攔阻","createTime":"2018-10-01T03:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T09:14:02.000Z","uid":22349,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"527ff8a818dae71a8cded547f2f8a828b2a36aa7","tid":843210,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:31:45.000Z","msg":"十．一黃金周假期已到，香港落馬洲管制站今日清晨「淪陷」！多名市民目擊今日清晨五時許，24小時通關的香港落馬洲管制站往香港方向疑因開放的汽車入境通道不足，導至過境私家車大塞車，有旅客報稱等候近兩小時仍未能入境，結果出現近200名內地旅客不滿塞車下落車步過中英橋企圖「行路入境」的奇景。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，這批心急入境的內地旅客，不少都是乘過境私家來港，準備前往大嶼山的香港國際機場乘飛機往外地旅遊。但屬禁區的中英橋只准過境車輛行駛，故這樣下車行走做是違反規定的，所以香港警察一度築起封鎖線，阻擱這批旅客步行入境，場面「壯觀」，幸未有釀成衝突。"},{"pid":"1bc18bec104ec03cdaa32b978993a8d431e5bb34","tid":843210,"uid":22349,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181001/large/1538363172_be5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181001%2Flarge%2F1538363172_be5d.jpg&h=f4ac6d70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97b041fd288c231691cf295286a88910b8d44310","tid":843210,"uid":22349,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181001/large/1538363206_fe24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181001%2Flarge%2F1538363206_fe24.jpg&h=c13b2ad2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181001/large/1538363172_96f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181001%2Flarge%2F1538363172_96f7.jpg&h=6d6683cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c581563ae154167ca97068adf98696541644582","tid":843210,"uid":132587,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.ettoday.net/images/36/